  "title": "Outdoor Sales Executive | Class 3/3A/3C | 5.5 Days | Up To $2.8K + Comm - 4461",
  "description": "<p><strong>Outdoor B2B Sales Executive (Aquatic Plants)</strong><br />Salary: Basic $2,200 + Commission <br />Working Days: Monday - Friday 9:00am - 6:00pm | Saturday 9:00am - 1:00pm<br />Location: Yishun Ind Park (Near to Canberra MRT)</p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Build relationship with the retailers and increase product offerings and shelf presence</li><li>Provide exceptional customer service and support to clients</li><li>Provide product training to staff in the stores</li><li>Meet/exceed sales targets.</li><li>Participate in roadshows and promotional events to create company/product awareness and generate sales.</li><li>Collaborate with Marketing on marketing efforts and promotions, and execute them with the retailers</li><li>Process customers’ purchase orders and liaising with Logistics team.</li><li>Work with Accounts to ensure timely collection of sales proceeds from customers.</li></ul><p><strong>Qualifications:</strong></p><ul><li>At least a GCE 'O' level certificate</li><li>Proven experience as a Sales Executive or in a similar sales role</li><li>Must possess Class 3/3A/3C Driving license</li></ul><p><br /><br /><strong>Email: supreme.jacksontan@gmail.com</strong></p><p><strong>Tan Yong Zhi (Jackson) | Reg: R24124461</strong></p><p><strong>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte. Ltd | EA No: 14C7279</strong></p>",
